#

Lentil and Sweet Potato Shepherd's Pie

55 min
$10.5
320 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

AmericanBritish

Course:

Main CourseVegetarian Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodHealthyEasy

Description

A comforting and nutritious twist on a classic shepherd's pie, featuring hearty lentils and creamy sweet potatoes.

Ingredients

  • lentils (cooked): 1 cup
  • sweet potatoes (peeled and cubed): 2 medium
  • vegetable broth: 1 cup
  • carrots (diced): 1 cup
  • onion (chopped): 1 medium
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • thyme (dried): 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • frozen peas: 1/2 cup
